      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i checked the bolts and they seem tight. the noise is like super consistent though, almost like a constant screeching every time the wheels move. it almost sounds... i dont know, kind of rhythmic and piercing? do you think it could be something stuck inside the assembly or maybe a part that wasn't seated right?",
