      "content": "i tried looking, but i can't really see anything obvious just by staring at it. it's just this weird, shrill noise that sounds almost like a... i don't know, a tiny scream? it's so high pitched it's actually kind of unsettling. is there anything else that makes a noise like that? like maybe something internal or something i wouldn't see just by looking at the bracket?",
